{"tid":636753,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"氣槍狂徒鋼珠射爆食肆玻璃","createTime":"2018-04-21T07:49:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-21T09:17:55.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"efacb4773b77c0c264244630634499929bc48329","tid":636753,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T07:49:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180421/20368209?_ga=2.136347696.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180421%2F20368209%3F_ga%3D2.136347696.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=8ixOoKLrRshC%2Fvc01r0nFiwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=d436b2d6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180421%2F20368209%3F_ga%3D2.136347696.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=a9a9bd43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180421/20368209?_ga=2.136347696.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n氣槍狂徒鋼珠射爆食肆玻璃<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180421/large/21la6p31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180421%2Flarge%2F21la6p31.jpg&h=a7598e55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■機動部隊警員昨到場調查。溫瑞麟攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】黃大仙出現氣槍狂徒，兩個月內3次以熟食亭為目標，前日下午5時許，狂徒再次射毀餐廳玻璃，幸無人受傷。警方到場撿獲4粒鋼珠，懷疑犯案者於熟食亭對面大廈用氣槍發射鋼珠，警方正調查3宗案件是否同一人所為。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兩個月三熟食亭中招<br />\n<br />\n現場為黃大仙竹園南邨熟食亭，前日下午5時許，熟食亭內一間餐廳，一塊約1米乘1.5米的牆身玻璃鏡突然破裂，職員發現報警。職員以白膠布貼在受損玻璃窗上，以防玻璃碎裂濺傷途人及食客。警方發現玻璃上留有破洞，並撿獲共4粒鋼珠，大批機動部隊警員（PTU）在對面黃大仙上邨詠善樓調查，封鎖大堂調查出入住客，部份警員走到附近山坡視察，惟未有發現。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息指，金屬珠懷疑是氣槍用的鋼珠，而上址過去兩個月已先後發生3次同類事件。據悉涉事餐廳開業7年，過去沒收過任何恐嚇，去年餐廳一幅玻璃亦曾突然爆裂，當時職員不以為意。警方正調查歹徒動機，與及是否同一人所為，案件由黃大仙警區重案組跟進。<br />\n<br />\n■記者溫瑞麟  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n原在女家凍肉大王店幫手　另起爐灶　 燒炭亡夫婦　與外家打對台輸身家"},{"pid":"b64e50987eda0c880baeb800da6a5f98d1400571","tid":636753,"uid":44291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T07:50:16.000Z","msg":"鎗王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb4c6e3eb3ebabb9cb71c15bcd3c82f91789bf1f","tid":636753,"uid":80140,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T07:50:44.000Z","msg":"係打都落旺角打大媽 無撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f84133d8a20a20eb7b8518b89d1a47704e6d5da5","tid":636753,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T07:56:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6bd85d0477ef453c5082955ea9a488fb8f4f43ad","tid":636753,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T09:17:55.000Z","msg":"泛民打手LIKLN<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/21/171754_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F21%2F171754_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=12d8efad&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}